text: int gcd ( int a , int b ) { int m = 0 , i , g = 0 , lcm = 1 ; m = b ; if ( a > b ) m = a ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= m ; i ++ ) { if ( ( a % i == 0 ) && ( b % i == 0 ) ) g = i ; } return g ; } int main ( ) { int a , b , t ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; int g , l ; if ( t >= 1 && t <= 1000 ) { for ( int i = 1 ; i <= t ; i ++ ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; if ( a >= 1 && a <= 1000000 && b >= 1 && b <= 1000000 ) { g = gcd ( a , b ) ; l = a * b / g ; printf ( "%d %d \n" , g , l ) ; } else exit ( 0 ) ; } } return 0 ; }
